Q6A Gemma4 LiteRT-LM NPU Runtime Patches

This repository contains source patches, scripts, and documentation for
running Gemma 4 E2B with LiteRT-LM on Radxa Dragon Q6A / Qualcomm QCS6490.

This repository does not redistribute:

- Qualcomm QAIRT/QNN runtime libraries
- Gemma model weights
- LiteRT-LM model containers (`.litertlm`)
- QNN context binaries

